snippet.textDisplay: I am not sure the end goal of coke studio Bangla, and I have nothing personal against sunidhi or arnob. But arnob needs to come out of the idea of placing his loved ones in the spot for the sake of limelight. This song could have been done by somebody else with much more compassion, even from our classical singers from west bengal could have done it hundred times better. Somehow someway we Asian never fail to break free from nepotism.
